data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"The source site reads as theatrical restaurant branding: blackened fire, lamb and Mediterranean provenance, uppercase navigation, rich food photography, and direct booking/menu/function paths. I’m turning that into a refined multi-page concept without changing the business facts."}

